  "body": "The difference between `rpcdaemon` and `restapi` is confusing.\r\n\r\n`restapi` takes the format of `--http.addr=\"0.0.0.0:9092\"`\r\n\r\n`rpcdaemon` requires the port to be specified separately `--http.addr=\"0.0.0.0\"` and `--http.port=9091`\r\n\r\nWould be nice if they were unified.",
